<Content>Good Hotel, I would stay there again. We Stayed for 4 Nights. Paid USD67 per night (Total, incl taxes). We got exactly what we wanted. Clean, MiniBar (used for refrig only), 1 Hugh bed, TV, AC/heat, Good part of town, walk to the subway, good restaurants close, clean bathroom, hot water with good pressure, tub. The room was a good size, not hugh, but sufficient for 2 people. The staff was very helpful. They had a good bar upstairs. All in all it was a very good experience. I would highly recommend it. I am really not sure why others wrote such poor reviews, I had no problems at all. This place was fine. For the money, it was great. No internet, Local phone calls HKD5 per call. 
